    <h2 id="Alexandra-AndrewAppointed">Alexandra Eveleigh and Andrew Turvey were appointed as Trustees</h2>
    <p>On <strong>4 April 2018</strong>, Alexandra Eveleigh and Andrew Turvey were appointed as Trustees of Free UK Genealogy. Alexandra is an archivist, whose PhD studied human transcription projects. Andrew Turvey has brought, from his professional background as an accountant, experience from his work with Wikidata.</p>

