    <h2>Earlier News about FreeBMD</h2>
    <p class="islet islet--bordered"> <strong>In the pipeline</strong>: two new pages are in preparation. One, our <strong>History page</strong> will summarise the progress of FreeBMD from its inception in 1988-89 and take the story forward to the end of 2014. It will suppliement this page which starts from 2015. The page will include material on our 10th Anniversary. The other page, <strong>Release Notes</strong> provides a summary of technical matters, such as the new release of transcriber tools — especially WinBMD and BMDVerify — and various enhancements to both the <em>FreeBMD search engine</em> and the quality control processes that we run on the FreeMBD databases.</p>

